<div class='row'>
  <div class="small-12 large-8 large-centered columns">
    <h2>Donation Receipt</h2>


    <h4>Donation Information:</h4>
    <p>Donated to: <%= current_campaign.candidate.name  %> </p>
    <p>Amount Donated: $<%= @donation.amount  %> </p>

    <p><%= @donor.name %>,</p>

    <p>  Thank you for contributing to my scholarship.  I am incredibly excited for this opportunity and I know it wouldn't be possible without your support.  I want to share my experience with you so please stop back often to see what I am up to!  Please see below how you can continue helping by nominating someone to receive a future just like I have.</p>

    <p>Thanks again,</p>
    <p><%=  current_campaign.candidate.name %></p>


    <h4>What Now?</h4>
    <p>Now that you have made a donation to our current campaign for <%= current_campaign.candidate.name  %>, we would like to invite you to nominate one of  current candidates for our next campaign.  Follow the link below to see a list of the current candidates and view their profile page to help narrow down who you would like to nominate.  </p>

    <%= link_to "See All Candidates", candidates_url, class: 'button'
    %>
  </div>
</div>